{"tid":301313,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪未出場已多人like 蔡思貝搏盡扮醜 網民負評：得個嘈字！","createTime":"2017-06-28T13:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T13:27:35.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb6fd7a594a2823d56181f44098189f45f86bd3","tid":301313,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"大台劇《踩過界》在剛剛過去兩晚終於播出，《壹》仔看了，覺得幾過癮，難怪有網民讚：「第一集感覺不差，一集來說有2.5個cases，幾緊湊。」不過比起劇集內容，網民似乎更熱衷於討論演員本身！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19510155_796937773820352_5013145427534397881_n.jpg?oh=d90a0974abc860295e99d7f75e82fd7c&amp;oe=5A0C717E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19510155_796937773820352_5013145427534397881_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dd90a0974abc860295e99d7f75e82fd7c%26oe%3D5A0C717E&h=c9460c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就演員演技方面，男主角王浩信似乎一早已經被視為演技派，做得好是意料之內，事關有網民這樣讚他：「王浩信做得好就預咗。」 <br />\n不過究竟好在哪，看過他演出的人有這樣評價：「王浩信真的做得很神似，連一些身體語言都做到足，其實好難演，很容易會過火，不過他handle到。」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19511249_796937893820340_2479467259871313511_n.jpg?oh=70f4473908a79ada72dc1cca768d754d&amp;oe=59D411BF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19511249_796937893820340_2479467259871313511_n.jpg%3Foh%3D70f4473908a79ada72dc1cca768d754d%26oe%3D59D411BF&h=5ba6f93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於另一男角張振朗，演技同樣有網民讚賞，不過對於他在第一集扮母狗叫那幕，其實很不好笑。 而討論最多的，就是女主角蔡思貝。雖然她今次哨牙扮醜的造型得到不少人欣賞，說她肯搏肯做，不介面形象身段，亦有人讚她演技持續進步中，但讚賞真的不多，反而針對她聲音的負皮，多得不能盡錄。 <br />\n「真是頂不順蔡思貝，演技完全配合不到，張大喉嚨嗌就等於凶狠嗎？成集得個嘈字。」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19598845_796938040486992_6866105764808504578_n.jpg?oh=855ec1748278d31231bb8bce20bf2dd5&amp;oe=59D01101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19598845_796938040486992_6866105764808504578_n.jpg%3Foh%3D855ec1748278d31231bb8bce20bf2dd5%26oe%3D59D01101&h=a09c46df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只能夠說，蔡思貝本身觀眾緣不好啦，因為同劇的朱千雪，雖然出場集數不多，但評價就和蔡思貝截然相反。 <br />\n「鍾意看朱千雪，她很自然，很舒服，不做作，又靚又有身材，又識做戲，學歷又高，好過新一代所謂花旦。」<br />\n <img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19511534_796937727153690_1714679084942286744_n.jpg?oh=f8095cc36802e71eba0878c764f11a40&amp;oe=5A0F6074\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19511534_796937727153690_1714679084942286744_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df8095cc36802e71eba0878c764f11a40%26oe%3D5A0F6074&h=eceaa450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩！朱千雪BB都未正式出場，人人都已經咁冧咁BUY佢，日後播到她著婚紗那幕，豈不看得人人心心眼，爭著幻想做她另一半？不過可惜，不知她讀完書畢業後，仍會否繼續拍劇呢？"},{"pid":"49ddfb907a136015158615540efdf0fd94939e6e","tid":301313,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"若有若無巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a335ae369f2a23d30119344e4fc4f2a03d798941","tid":301313,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:44:28.000Z","msg":"事實吖嘛<br />\n連學歷都爭人成截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdabaca7dde7b45ede4c401fc458a00914426388","tid":301313,"uid":342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"千雪bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ed0080d742c797f5e4a8f458f9f5b5028e925","tid":301313,"uid":116390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實吖嘛<br />\n連學歷都爭人成截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估個個都可以兩個月讀完degree架？<br />\n仲要係外國大學呀"},{"pid":"4833ec76afa90dfc2de9d60ecbb1659b4d59a6fa","tid":301313,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"朱千雪係正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d454ed5670ed12cd9686702f3c406d35b5122c6c","tid":301313,"uid":91620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"佢話做我老婆 唔再拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791f851feb9219426e565dec5e62f5382f7906cb","tid":301313,"uid":3535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"靚湯真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1de99da6087f4ae38006e15f56dd0373c55c7b","tid":301313,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"點解無提Ali<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a070d0c0908db55618d4505f7f2d77aecc0c9301","tid":301313,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實吖嘛<br />\n連學歷都爭人成截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估個個都可以兩個月讀完degree架？<br />\n仲要係外國大學呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港周街都係大學生啦"},{"pid":"27879a3ce3ed009ce31fdb661a8f586ed3f362bf","tid":301313,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:27:35.000Z","msg":"雪雪已經29歲 快啲拍拖啦～"}]}